data.text:
By Paul Goodman

Follow Paul on Twitter.

Alan Keen, the Labour MP for Feltham and Heston, has died aged 73. We will write more about the consequent by-election in due course, but it is right now simply to send commiserations to his family. His wife, Ann Keen, was MP for Brentford and Isleworth from 19997-2010.
